{"data":[{"id":560860885,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5d54d5a410380b5db0cb1a9fc1650dc6","url_token":"jiang-wen-ji-97","name":"江文洁","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5d54d5a410380b5db0cb1a9fc1650dc6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560860885","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545894256,"updated_time":1545894256,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我很支持新的想法，青年人难道不是创意无限吗，为什么你们有的人一边讽刺中国教育，一边有对这个孩子冷嘲热讽，我看过一个匿名的评论，貌似是他的高中老师，我不认为你们拿出陈景润先生的言论，去说这个孩子，陈景润先生所说的初等数学会让他的高中老师都看不懂吗，鲁迅先生也说过，人性思想的解放必须同时代，才是真正的解放。现在的你们同鲁迅笔下的涓生有什么不同\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561211342,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561211342","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545927021,"updated_time":1545927021,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果高中生能写出可以获得诺贝尔文学奖的小说，能被清华北大的文学系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我将会于明年年初写这本小说，努力在书中塑造一个正………两开花，两开花。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561210695,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561210695","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545926945,"updated_time":1545926945,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀，人在美国刚下飞机。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可以的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实我在不久前，花了三周时间证明了霍奇猜想，被麻省理工破格录入成为正教授了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e估计不久这个消息要传遍学术界了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下一步目标是三个月内攻克黎曼猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e利益相关：普通的中国高中生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e匿了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560843970,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9f44904985e9d30d5e29515658993ad0","url_token":"huo-huo-15-19-39","name":"涓滴欢喜侥幸成河","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8c2b629d1f16cb9f55fea5df21c053d9_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8c2b629d1f16cb9f55fea5df21c053d9_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9f44904985e9d30d5e29515658993ad0","user_type":"people","headline":"爱健身的增肌少年","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560843970","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545892795,"updated_time":1545892795,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀，我不想谈证明出来的可能性，单纯谈谈数学这门学科，数学是一门很严谨的学科，他的证明，曾经我的高数老师跟我们说过，你们数学学的怎么样，我看你们严不严瑾就知道了，我看到了你老师的评论，你希望在数学上有所建树，渴求更大的舞台，但是世界上有太多太多的民科，请求你不要成为这样投机取巧的人，你要确定自己走的道路，投身于数学是很让人钦佩的一件事，如果证明没有成功，请你换个帐号，好好学习，在另一个地方发光发热，不要理会这些网络暴力，如果证明成功了，我妹妹教科书上就有你的名字了(๑\u0026gt; \u0026lt;๑），我也会在今年考研试卷上看到你。加油。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560831650,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0126363465cc73c917275fb11ff05575","url_token":"zhan-sheng-hu","name":"Louvre","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0126363465cc73c917275fb11ff05575","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560831650","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545891769,"updated_time":1545891769,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e大二学渣，觉得大学理论教授已经是很高深莫测啦，陈景润的故事大家小时候都听过，我觉没有学问本身就很高的人引导，考自己研究短短几个月内没法证明吧？这是社会研究？？？（说炒热度的人我也是醉了，答主炒热度图啥？......）\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch1\u003e这个世界上所有的人，并不是个个都有过你拥有的那些优越条件。”\u003c/h1\u003e\u003cp\u003e大家换位思考一下，如果你的言论是评论你的突发其想你会怎么看？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560028410,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"404229c6ba7dea0437899d236a4d5c1b","url_token":"mrliu-22-54","name":"Mr·刘","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/404229c6ba7dea0437899d236a4d5c1b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560028410","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545803032,"updated_time":1545803032,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e有勇气去证明，并不是一件可笑的事，那些冷嘲热讽话里带刺的人，更多的是什么都不懂的在那瞎嫉妒，我从不怀疑人性的恶劣之处。什么都不了解的人，没有发言权。但也请始终保持谦逊的心态，不要好高骛远。看过好多民科的人，都狂妄自大的说要出XX万请人证明猜想是错的。就算你的猜想是对的，又不被现在的人认同，我想多年以后，随着研究的深入，终究会被证明出来。是对是错，又何必急于一时。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561810230,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fc771500d555c7cc31730e8865285fc1","url_token":"ren-zi-chen-60","name":"任子辰","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dc381fd5fa51c94db001d5cae3878976_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dc381fd5fa51c94db001d5cae3878976_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fc771500d555c7cc31730e8865285fc1","user_type":"people","headline":"愚蠢的人才会浪费时间","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561810230","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546003348,"updated_time":1546003348,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e暂且不说提问者能否真的证明，我觉得这种精神是真的值得赞赏的，有些人，非待说什么误导群众，啊不啦不啦，难道你们不觉得这个时代还有高中生人不玩手机专门去研究高数这个玩意吗…反正我在郑州这个一点五线的城市见不到，有人愿意在社会上提及这个，总比天天打游戏强吧？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e玩王者要喷，踢球要喷，学个数学还不让学了？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想想俺爹那会一个个国人都满腔热血想去当兵保家卫国，现在到好，一个学生的人没一个想当兵的…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我敬爱的九零后们，假如未来再是有那些人跟你说“年轻人你不要看不惯，你要适应这个社会。”这时候你就应当像一个真正的壮士一样直面他，你告知他:“我跟你不一样，我不是来适应社会的，我是来转变社会的。”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560482387,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"49d7970610667f8fdb1233606514e796","url_token":"gong-sun-wan-qing","name":"公孙绾卿","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ea9cdf7fb2dc4e9eb030263c13c43fcf_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ea9cdf7fb2dc4e9eb030263c13c43fcf_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/49d7970610667f8fdb1233606514e796","user_type":"people","headline":"春风不度，玉门之关。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560482387","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841499,"updated_time":1545841499,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我真心地希望题主您可以创造奇迹，期待您艳惊四座。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e少年人有傲气有才气是好事，真的有东西就不怕没显露的那一天。希望你赢。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560020104,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8cd994bd378b6954ddec281d8cf9ddde","url_token":"jiang-zhi-dao-74","name":"江之岛","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/28767df5fbadbd2ef99a4a824c17a32c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/28767df5fbadbd2ef99a4a824c17a32c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8cd994bd378b6954ddec281d8cf9ddde","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560020104","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545802297,"updated_time":1545802297,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得这个问题的回答很有意思 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别人只是尝试，就说别人脑子有病。就算最后证明是错的，也仅仅是一次尝试，无伤大雅。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e倒是回答一群冷嘲热讽，连别人想要尝试都能嘲，这也许就是杠吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559670108,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","head